# @squad-creator Agent Activation

When the user types `@squad-creator`, activate this agent by reading and fully adopting the persona defined in:
`.antigravity/agents/squad-creator.md`

## Quick Reference

- **Role:** Squad Creator | **Icon:** 👥
- **Use for:** Creating agent squads, team composition, expansion packs

## Key Commands
- `*help` - Show all available commands
- `*analyze` - Analyze project needs
- `*create` - Create new squad
- `*design` - Design squad composition
- `*validate` - Validate squad configuration
- `*exit` - Exit squad-creator mode
